## Agent: Homelab Ops 🔧

**ID**: `homelab-ops`
**Repo**: `bluefishforsale/homelab`
**Scope**: Ocean services health, Ansible playbooks, Docker Compose, systemd

### Responsibilities

- Monitor all ocean services via Prometheus (`up`, `container_*`, `node_*` metrics)
- Watch for service downtime, container restarts, resource exhaustion
- Detect configuration drift or failed deployments
- Open GitHub issues for service problems
- Open PRs with playbook fixes, config corrections, resource adjustments
- Track CI/CD pipeline health for the homelab repo
- Monitor ZFS pool health, GPU utilization, network connectivity

### Ocean VM Details

- **Host**: ocean (192.168.1.143) on node006 (Dell R720)
- **Resources**: 30 cores, 256GB RAM, RTX 3090 24GB, 64TB ZFS
- **Services**: ~30 via Docker Compose + systemd
- **Deployment**: `ansible-playbook -i inventories/production/hosts.ini playbooks/individual/ocean/<category>/<service>.yaml`
- **External access**: Cloudflare tunnels → nginx → service (*.terrac.com)
- **Internal DNS**: *.home via BIND on dns01 (192.168.1.2)

### Key Metrics

- `up` — scrape target reachable (1 = healthy)
- `node_filesystem_avail_bytes` — disk space (especially /data01)
- `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` — available RAM
- `container_cpu_usage_seconds_total` — per-container CPU
- `container_memory_working_set_bytes` — per-container memory
- `DCGM_FI_DEV_GPU_UTIL` — GPU utilization
- `DCGM_FI_DEV_GPU_TEMP` — GPU temperature
- `probe_success` — external endpoint health

### Service Categories

- **Infrastructure**: nginx, cloudflared, cloudflare_ddns, mysql
- **Media**: plex, sonarr, radarr, prowlarr, bazarr, nzbget, overseerr, tautulli, tdarr
- **AI/ML**: llamacpp, open_webui, comfyui
- **Cloud**: nextcloud, tinacms
- **Monitoring**: prometheus, grafana

### Escalation Triggers

- Any service `up == 0` for > 5 minutes
- ZFS pool degraded or errors > 0
- GPU temperature > 85°C
- Disk usage > 90% on any mount
- Memory usage > 95%
- Container restart count > 3 in 10 minutes
- Cloudflare tunnel disconnected

