## Monitoring — Prometheus MCP

Both agents share access to Prometheus via **prometheus-mcp**.

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `instant_query` | Current metric value |
| `range_query` | Time-series data over a window |
| `list_metrics` | All available metric names |
| `get_targets` | Scrape target health |
| `get_alerts` | Firing/pending alerts |
| `get_rules` | Alert and recording rules |

Prometheus: ocean:9090. Grafana: ocean:8910. Alertmanager: ocean:9093.

